Title: Incorrect version tags linked to external repository
Description: A security incident caused a number of incorrect version tags to be pushed to the Parse Server repository.
AffectedVersions: All versions starting from 4.0.0 before 4.5.2, all versions starting from 4.6.0 before 4.10.0
NotImpacted: All versions before 4.0.0, all versions starting from 4.5.2 before 4.6.0, all versions starting from 4.10.0
